<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<style>
			body { background-color: #0d1012; /* Matches your dashboard
			background */ color: #fafafa; font-family: -apple-system,
			BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif; margin: 0;
			padding: 40px 0; } .container { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;
			background-color: #14171a; /* Matches your card background */
			border: 1px solid #27272a; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; }
			.logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff;
			margin-bottom: 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; }
			.brand-icon { color: #ee8d45; /* Your orange accent color */
			margin-right: 8px; } h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600;
			margin-top: 0; } p { color: #a1a1aa; /* Muted text color */
			line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; } .btn { display: inline-block;
			background-color: #ee8d45; /* Your "Add Website" orange button */
			color: #ffffff !important; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px;
			text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; margin: 24px 0; } .footer {
			margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid #27272a;
			font-size: 12px; color: #71717a; } .highlight { color: #ffffff; } a{
			color: #00a2ff; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="logo">
				<span
					class="brand-icon"
					style="
						outline: 2px solid white;
						border-radius: 100vw;
						outline-offset: 2px;
					"
				>
					<svg
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						width="32"
						height="32"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						xmlns:bx="https://boxy-svg.com"
					>
						<defs>
							<bx:export>
								<bx:file format="svg" />
							</bx:export>
						</defs>
						<ellipse
							style="
								stroke-width: 0px;
								paint-order: fill;
								stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);
							"
							cx="12"
							cy="11.953"
							rx="11.906"
							ry="11.906"
						/>
						<g
							fill="none"
							stroke="#888888"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							transform="matrix(0.8, 0, 0, 0.8, 2.4, 2.35)"
						>
							<path
								d="M17 19a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-2a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2a1 1 0 0 1-1 1zm0 2v-2"
								style="stroke: rgb(255, 255, 255)"
							/>
							<path
								d="M19 14V6.5a1 1 0 0 0-7 0v11a1 1 0 0 1-7 0V10m16 11v-2M3 5V3"
								style="stroke: rgb(255, 255, 255)"
							/>
							<path
								d="M4 10a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2zm3-5V3"
								style="stroke: rgb(255, 255, 255)"
							/>
						</g>
					</svg>
				</span>
				WebStat
			</div>

			<p>Hi <span class="highlight">{{name}}</span>,</p>
			<p style="color: white;">
				This is a quick notification to let you know that the password
				for your WebStat account ({{email}}) was successfully changed on
				{{date}}
				.<br />
				<strong>If this was you:</strong>
				You can safely ignore this email. No further action is required.
				<br />
				<strong>If this was NOT you:</strong>
				Your account security may be compromised. Please take the
				following steps immediately:
				<ol>
					<li>Reset your password using our Forgot Password page.</li>
					<li>Ensure your email account is secure.</li>
					<li>Contact our support team if you notice any suspicious
						activity in your monitoring dashboards.</li>
				</ol>
				For your security, we have logged you out of all other active
				sessions.
				<br />Stay safe, The WebStat Team
			</p>

			<div class="footer">
				Sent on
				{{date}}<br />

			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>